data.description: If you love windows and you love space then welcome home. This home has the most beautiful front window and a huge living room. No need for any blinds, the window has an outside tint so you can soak up all the sun but no one can see in ever. Next, hold on to your seats, there's a perfect glam room space outside the primary bedroom. Or, divide the space and make it an office/gym or even a game/movie room. It can be whatever you want it to be. Including private since the primary is located at the back of the house with the additional bedrooms at the front. The front porch is darling, perfect for morning coffee and the backyard is massive, perfect for family gatherings. Once we get rain and grass again of course. Also, LOCATION-LOCATION-LOCATION. You're five minutes to Ft. Sam, The Pearl, Downtown. It's cheaper to Uber to downtown than to park. Don't miss this excellent opportunity for you new home, check it out today!!!
